EventAction_LuaScript.Description: 加载函数
EventAction_LuaScript.ScriptText:
--添加巡飞弹发射车单元 local Anti_RadiationLauncher = ScenEdit_GetUnit({name='反辐射巡飞弹发射车', guid='11e2bb04-066a-4356-a3b2-f2defd0f2d5d'}) local Anti_RadiationLauncher = ScenEdit_GetUnit({name='红外巡飞弹发射车', guid='1d834270-3e6b-4d4f-b14e-596cb9f525a4'}) --反辐射巡飞弹列表 local AntiradiationCruiseMissil={} --攻击建筑物巡飞弹列表 local CruiseMissilesAttackingBuilding={} --攻击移动车辆巡飞弹列表 local AttackingMobileVehicleCruiseMissil={} --攻击通信节点巡飞弹列表 local AttackingCommunicationNodeCruiseMissil={}
--发射巡飞弹 UAVType=1为反辐射巡飞弹，UAVType=2为攻击建筑物，UAVType=3为攻击移动车辆，UAVType == "4"为攻击通信节点 function ReleaseUAV(unit,sideName,UAVType,index,high) --如果发射巡飞弹的发射车不为空 if unit~=nil then if UAVType == "1" then --添加反辐射巡飞弹 UAVUnit = ScenEdit_AddUnit({side=sideName,unitname="反辐射巡飞弹 #0"..index,type="Air",dbid=1004964,latitude=unit.latitude,longitude=unit.longitude,loadoutid=1025689,altitude=high}) --将反辐射巡飞弹加入到列表中 table.insert(AntiradiationCruiseMissil,UAVUnit) elseif UAVType == "2" then --添加攻击建筑物巡飞弹 UAVUnit =ScenEdit_AddUnit({side=sideName,unitname="攻击建筑物巡飞弹 #0"..index,type="Air",dbid=1004965,latitude=unit.latitude,longitude=unit.longitude,loadoutid=1025690,altitude=high}) --将攻击建筑物巡飞弹加入到列表中 table.insert(CruiseMissilesAttackingBuilding,UAVUnit) elseif UAVType == "3" then --添加攻击移动车辆巡飞弹 UAVUnit =ScenEdit_AddUnit({side=sideName,unitname="攻击移动车辆巡飞弹 #0"..index,type="Air",dbid=1004965,latitude=unit.latitude,longitude=unit.longitude,loadoutid=1025690,altitude=high}) --将攻击移动车辆巡飞弹加入到列表中 table.insert(AttackingMobileVehicleCruiseMissil,UAVUnit) elseif UAVType == "4" then --添加攻击移动车辆巡飞弹 UAVUnit =ScenEdit_AddUnit({side=sideName,unitname="攻击通信节点巡飞弹 #0"..index,type="Air",dbid=1004965,latitude=unit.latitude,longitude=unit.longitude,loadoutid=1025690,altitude=high}) --将攻击通信节点巡飞弹加入到列表中 table.insert(AttackingCommunicationNodeCruiseMissil,UAVUnit)
end end end
--巡飞弹发射，num为发射数量，high为高度，CruiseFlyMissileType为巡飞弹类型 --CruiseFlyMissileType="1"为反辐射巡飞弹，CruiseFlyMissileType="2"为攻击建筑物，CruiseFlyMissileType="3"为攻击移动车辆,CruiseFlyMissileType="3"为攻击通信节点，Anti_RadiationLauncher为发射巡飞弹的单元 function CruiseFlyMissileLaunch(Anti_RadiationLauncher,num,high,CruiseFlyMissileType) for index=1,num do print("index = "..index) print(Anti_RadiationLauncher.name) print(Anti_RadiationLauncher.latitude) print(Anti_RadiationLauncher.longitude) print("CruiseFlyMissileType = "..CruiseFlyMissileType) print("high = "..high) ReleaseUAV(Anti_RadiationLauncher,"红方",CruiseFlyMissileType,index,high) end end
--反辐射无人机是否开火 function IsFired(unit) if unit.loadout[1].loadout_weapons[1].wpn_current == 0 then return true else return false end end --反辐射无人机变成导弹后的处理，自毁 function AntiradiationUAVToMissile() if #(AntiradiationCruiseMissil) ~= 0 then for i=1,#(AntiradiationCruiseMissil) do if i<=#(AntiradiationCruiseMissil) then if IsFired(AntiradiationCruiseMissil[i])== true then DeleteUnit(AntiradiationCruiseMissil[i]) table.remove(AntiradiationCruiseMissil,i) end end end end end
--攻击建筑物无人机变成导弹后的处理，自毁 function AttackingBuildingUAVToMissile() if #(CruiseMissilesAttackingBuilding) ~= 0 then for i=1,#(CruiseMissilesAttackingBuilding) do if i<=#(CruiseMissilesAttackingBuilding) then if IsFired(CruiseMissilesAttackingBuilding[i])== true then DeleteUnit(CruiseMissilesAttackingBuilding[i]) table.remove(CruiseMissilesAttackingBuilding,i) end end end end end
--攻击移动车辆无人机变成导弹后的处理，自毁 function AttackingMobileVehicleUAVToMissile() if #(AttackingMobileVehicleCruiseMissil) ~= 0 then for i=1,#(AttackingMobileVehicleCruiseMissil) do if i<=#(AttackingMobileVehicleCruiseMissil) then if IsFired(AttackingMobileVehicleCruiseMissil[i])== true then DeleteUnit(AttackingMobileVehicleCruiseMissil[i]) table.remove(AttackingMobileVehicleCruiseMissil,i) end end end end end
--攻击通信节点无人机变成导弹后的处理，自毁 function AttackingCommunicationNodeCruiseUAVToMissile() if #(AttackingCommunicationNodeCruiseMissil) ~= 0 then for i=1,#(AttackingCommunicationNodeCruiseMissil) do if i<=#(AttackingCommunicationNodeCruiseMissil) then if IsFired(AttackingCommunicationNodeCruiseMissil[i])== true then DeleteUnit(AttackingCommunicationNodeCruiseMissil[i]) table.remove(AttackingCommunicationNodeCruiseMissil,i) end end end end end
--删除单元 function DeleteUnit(unit) ScenEdit_DeleteUnit({name=unit.name, guid=unit.guid}) end
